==Japanese==
===Alternative spellings===
*[[Kanji]]: [[土降る]]
*[[Kana]]: [[つちふる]]
*[[Romaji]]: [[tsuchifuru]], [[tutihuru]]
===Etymology===
[[土]] ''tsuchi'' "earth" + [[降る]] ''furu'' "to fall (rain, snow)"
===Verb===
{{wikipedia|Asian Dust}}
'''[[霾]]る'''

# For [[Asian Dust]] to fall like rain.
